    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>
PrinterToolkit is a complete PowerShell-based Windows printer management solution for IT administrators, helpdesk technicians, and power users.

Features:
- Printer Inventory & Status — enumerate all printers with detailed status
- IPP Discovery — Internet Printing Protocol support detection and validation
- Driver Intelligence — Type 3 vs Type 4 detection, export, restore, INF install
- Share Management — enable/disable sharing, set permissions, switch transports
- Android Printing — Mopria Print Service compatibility wizard and connection strings
- Automatic Repair — 8-step repair workflow with full backup and rollback
- Diagnostics — 17-check network validation, firewall/registry/service snapshots
- Reporting — professional HTML reports, JSON/CSV exports, compliance checks
- Diagnostic Bundle — ZIP archive with 12 diagnostic sections
    </description>
    <summary>Enterprise Windows printer troubleshooting and management toolkit for PowerShell.</summary>
    <tags>printer printing diagnostics windows troubleshooting ipp mopria android powershell spooler driver network repair report</tags>
    <packageSourceUrl>https://github.com/00AstroGit00/windows-printer-toolkit</packageSourceUrl>
    <docsUrl>https://github.com/00AstroGit00/windows-printer-toolkit/blob/main/README.md</docsUrl>
    <bugTrackerUrl>https://github.com/00AstroGit00/windows-printer-toolkit/issues</bugTrackerUrl>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/00AstroGit00/windows-printer-toolkit/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>
